2666783', description='Dive into this energizing full-body circuit, designed to boost strength and endurance! 💪 1️⃣ Squat Jacks (30 secs): Start strong with this heart-pumping full-body exercise. 🕒 Rest (15 secs) 2️⃣ Mountain Climber with Twist (30 secs): Next, challenge your core with a twist. 🕒 Rest (15 secs) 3️⃣ Bear Crawl (30 secs): Finish with a total body challenge. Every move counts in this strength-building crawl. 🕒 Rest (15 secs) 🔄 Repeat all three exercises for 4 rounds. Each exercise is 30 seconds with a 15-second rest in between. #bodyweightworkout #bodyweighttraining #HomeWorkouts #NoEquipmentNeeded ', author='bodyweightexercises'), VideoModel(video_id='7516302669653249311', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@giovanni_fiderio/video/7516302669653249311', description='Helping busy people get lean 💪 No gym. Just bodyweight. DM “START” for your plan 📲 . . . . . #homeworkout #calisthenics #fatloss #leanphysique #bodyweighttraining #reels #fitnesscoach #fyp #explore #diet', author='giovanni_fiderio'), VideoModel(video_id='7567347318878424351', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@gymfts/video/7567347318878424351', description='💯💪Highly effective fat-burning at-home bodyweight workout: 9 exercises, enough for six months of training! Save this and start practicing! #home #workout #exercises #fitness #gym ', author='gymfts'), VideoModel(video_id='7567448803427601686', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@romantrains/video/7567448803427601686', description='Build a strong core from home 🔥 No equipment. No excuses. Just 5 simple moves for your abs, every area covered 👇 1️⃣ AbsCrunch Reach (3x12-15) 2️⃣ Leg Raises (3x12) 3️⃣ Heel Touches (3x15) 4️⃣ Plank Crunch (3x12) 5️⃣ Plank Hold (3x20-30 sec.) #absworkout #homeworkout #coreworkout #fitnessmotivation #bodyweighttraining ', author='romantrains'), VideoModel(video_id='7525352611705310495', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@tyfu_ng1/video/7525352611705310495', description='Body weight 2 min legs workout ⚡️ #viral #fypシ #legs #gymtok #trendin