th one stone - strength, flexibility, endurance. I love to train my body in a versatile and varied way. Do you also change your training to have a balanced strength and a supple body? 😀💯💪🤸🏽\u200d♂️😎 LIKE 🙏 TAG 👍  SAVE ✅ [Werbung/ad]  my Yoga mat…the best on the market in my opinion - link in my BIO🤸🏽\u200d♂️😀 #f#findyoursuperpowerm#movementismedicineb#bodyweights#strengthandconditioningb#bodyweightwarriorf#fitnessisalifestylem#moveyourbodya#animalmovesa#animalflowf#fitfamdeutschlandy#youareyourowngymf#functionalworkoutm#movementflowg#gymsharkg#gymshark66g#gymsharkathlete#c#connectwithyourbodyh#holisticlivingm#mandukaf#fitover50k#körpergewichtstraining#b#bodyweighttrainingg#getleanyogadudes', author='the.spiritbody.architect'), VideoModel(video_id='7505452959258529046', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@yesuispedro/video/7505452959258529046', description='TRY THIS BODYWEIGHT HYPERTROPHIC EXERCISE #gym #calisthenics ', author='yesuispedro'), VideoModel(video_id='7554778320592702734', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@dsymonefit/video/7554778320592702734', description='Body weight squats build strength you can use every day.    heels down, knees track toes, chest tall. 3 sets of 10–15 reps anywhere, anytime. 💾 save this for your next workout. #bodyweightsquats #bodyweighttraining #fitness #legday #workouttips ', author='dsymonefit'), VideoModel(video_id='7421077668679978258', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@squatcouple/video/7421077668679978258', description='📌UPPER BODY AT HOME | 4 Bodyweight Exercises👌 No Equipment? No Problem!🫡👇 ▸ Push-Ups – 3 sets x 12-15 reps   ▸ Pike Push-Ups – 3 sets x 10-12 reps   ▸ Close Grip Push-Ups – 3 sets x 8-10 reps   ▸ Mountain Climbers – 3 sets x 30-45 sec *30-45 sec rest between sets SAVE, SHARE & TRY!✌️ . 📲Download our fitness app : www.squatcouple.app 📲ดาวน์โหลดโปรแกรมออกกำลังกายในแอปได้ที่ : www.squatcouple.app', author='squatcouple'), VideoModel(video_id='7307049065202666783', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@bodyweightexercises/video/730704906520