ase SiX  #mobilitytraining #mma #martialarts #movementprep #jointmobility #rangeofmotion #coordination #bodyweighttraining', author='steph.rose.phase6'), VideoModel(video_id='7300150909928082731', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@fitburner/video/7300150909928082731', description='Nine Full Body Workouts For women. #fullbodyworkout #bodyweightworkout #weightlossworkout #fatloss #fatburningworkouts', author='fitburner'), VideoModel(video_id='7391173677167021343', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@elikabang/video/7391173677167021343', description='No equipments needed, we getting comfortable with our bodyweight #fullbodyworkout #athomeworkout ', author='elikabang'), VideoModel(video_id='7443838939040894238', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@fitcircuits/video/7443838939040894238', description='20 Minute HIIT Circuit 🔥 . Save | Share | Try ✅ . #fitcircuits #hiitworkout #cardio #hiit  #bodyweight #bodyweightworkout #fitness #aerobic #homeworkout #lunges #fullbodyworkout #workout #florida ', author='fitcircuits'), VideoModel(video_id='7482043127444868382', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@anthonycarlo_1/video/7482043127444868382', description='CIRCUIT THAT DELIVERS🔥 #hiit #hiitworkout #cardio #cardioworkout #bodyweight #strengthtraining ', author='anthonycarlo_1'), VideoModel(video_id='7306923631651638560', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@leo.moves/video/7306923631651638560', description='The perfect workout to do anywhere, anytime! 🔥 #workoutmotivation #bodyweightexercises #bodyweighttraining #coreworkout ', author='leo.moves'), VideoModel(video_id='7502482004970130696', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@addyshaqeeraaz/video/7502482004970130696', description='Beginner starts somewhere and your day is today 🤍 wearing @AYBL my discount code “ADDY10” to save 10% during check out #workoutroutine #bodyweightworkout #bodyweightexercises #bodyweighttraining #easyexercises #beginnerworkout #beginner #fyp #gymtok #fullbodyworkout #fullbody #exerciseathome #ayblathlete #fitness #workoutmotivation #onlinefi