s with one stone - strength, flexibility, endurance. I love to train my body in a versatile and varied way. Do you also change your training to have a balanced strength and a supple body? 😀💯💪🤸🏽\u200d♂️😎 LIKE 🙏 TAG 👍  SAVE ✅ [Werbung/ad]  my Yoga mat…the best on the market in my opinion - link in my BIO🤸🏽\u200d♂️😀 #f#findyoursuperpowerm#movementismedicineb#bodyweights#strengthandconditioningb#bodyweightwarriorf#fitnessisalifestylem#moveyourbodya#animalmovesa#animalflowf#fitfamdeutschlandy#youareyourowngymf#functionalworkoutm#movementflowg#gymsharkg#gymshark66g#gymsharkathlete#c#connectwithyourbodyh#holisticlivingm#mandukaf#fitover50k#körpergewichtstraining#b#bodyweighttrainingg#getleanyogadudes', author='the.spiritbody.architect'), VideoModel(video_id='7505452959258529046', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@yesuispedro/video/7505452959258529046', description='TRY THIS BODYWEIGHT HYPERTROPHIC EXERCISE #gym #calisthenics ', author='yesuispedro'), VideoModel(video_id='7554778320592702734', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@dsymonefit/video/7554778320592702734', description='Body weight squats build strength you can use every day.    heels down, knees track toes, chest tall. 3 sets of 10–15 reps anywhere, anytime. 💾 save this for your next workout. #bodyweightsquats #bodyweighttraining #fitness #legday #workouttips ', author='dsymonefit'), VideoModel(video_id='7421077668679978258', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@squatcouple/video/7421077668679978258', description='📌UPPER BODY AT HOME | 4 Bodyweight Exercises👌 No Equipment? No Problem!🫡👇 ▸ Push-Ups – 3 sets x 12-15 reps   ▸ Pike Push-Ups – 3 sets x 10-12 reps   ▸ Close Grip Push-Ups – 3 sets x 8-10 reps   ▸ Mountain Climbers – 3 sets x 30-45 sec *30-45 sec rest between sets SAVE, SHARE & TRY!✌️ . 📲Download our fitness app : www.squatcouple.app 📲ดาวน์โหลดโปรแกรมออกกำลังกายในแอปได้ที่ : www.squatcouple.app', author='squatcouple'), VideoModel(video_id='7307049065202666783', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@bodyweightexercises/video/7307049065202666783', description='Dive into this energizing full-body circuit, designed to boost strength and endurance! 💪 1️⃣ Squat Jacks (30 secs): Start strong with this heart-pumping full-body exercise. 🕒 Rest (15 secs) 2️⃣ Mountain Climber with Twist (30 secs): Next, challenge your core with a twist. 🕒 Rest (15 secs) 3️⃣ Bear Crawl (30 secs): Finish with a total body challenge. Every move counts in this strength-building crawl. 🕒 Rest (15 secs) 🔄 Repeat all three exercises for 4 rounds. Each exercise is 30 seconds with a 15-second rest in between. #bodyweightworkout #bodyweighttraining #HomeWorkouts #NoEquipmentNeeded ', author='bodyweightexercises'), VideoModel(video_id='7516302669653249311', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@giovanni_fiderio/video/7516302669653249311', description='Helping busy people get lean 💪 No gym. Just bodyweight. DM “START” for your plan 📲 . . . . . #homeworkout #calisthenics #fatloss #leanphysique #bodyweighttraining #reels #fitnesscoach #fyp #explore #diet', author='giovanni_fiderio'), VideoModel(video_id='7567347318878424351', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@gymfts/video/7567347318878424351', description='💯💪Highly effective fat-burning at-home bodyweight workout: 9 exercises, enough for six months of training! Save this and start practicing! #home #workout #exercises #fitness #gym ', author='gymfts'), VideoModel(video_id='7567448803427601686', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@romantrains/video/7567448803427601686', description='Build a strong core from home 🔥 No equipment. No excuses. Just 5 simple moves for your abs, every area covered 👇 1️⃣ AbsCrunch Reach (3x12-15) 2️⃣ Leg Raises (3x12) 3️⃣ Heel Touches (3x15) 4️⃣ Plank Crunch (3x12) 5️⃣ Plank Hold (3x20-30 sec.) #absworkout #homeworkout #coreworkout #fitnessmotivation #bodyweighttraining ', author='romantrains'), VideoModel(video_id='7525352611705310495', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@tyfu_ng1/video/7525352611705310495', description='Body weight 2 min legs workout ⚡️ #viral #fypシ #legs #gymtok #tre